1959;;Upstairs and Downstairs;;British;;Ralph Thomas;;Michael Craig, Anne Heywood;;comedy;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Upstairs_and_Downstairs;;Richard Barry marries Kate, daughter of his boss, Mansfield. Mansfield tells Richard he needs to take over the entertaining for their film so Richard decides to hire a servant.Their first hire, the Italian Maria, ends disastrously when she keeps inviting sailors over to their house to party.They eventually hire Ingrid.